            "explanation": { "en": "\"Navê min ... e\" is the pattern for saying your name. The name goes in the blank.", "de": "\"Navê min ... e\" ist das Muster, um seinen Namen zu sagen. Der Name kommt in die Lücke." }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "1-1-08",
          "type": "matching",
          "orderIndex": 7,
